name: D'Addario Pro-Winder String Winder and Cutter
reviews: great little tool. I've been doing a lot of string restringing lately so i went for it. Really happy with it. you can also cut strings with it... pretty handy

name: D'Addario Pro-Winder String Winder and Cutter
reviews: I ordered this tool to assist with my first attempt at re-stringing a guitar after reading the reviews.  The tool was great for getting an accurate clip on the strings to keep things tidy and functional.  Lightweight and easy to use.

name: D'Addario Pro-Winder String Winder and Cutter
reviews: Love that fact that it is a string cutter, a bridge pin remover and a tuning peg winder all in one. Product came on time and the package was nicely done. Highly recommend this to any acoustic guitarists who wishes for more convenience when it comes to regular guitar maintenance.

name: D'Addario Pro-Winder String Winder and Cutter
reviews: Winder easy to use, and cuts string ends cleanly.

name: D'Addario Pro-Winder String Winder and Cutter
reviews: Works a treat.  I am new to stringing guitars and it made it easy for me.

name: D'Addario Pro-Winder String Winder and Cutter
reviews: Only got it for the string cutter part and it cuts them on my steel string easily. No complaints

name: D'Addario Pro-Winder String Winder and Cutter
reviews: No more having to carry wire cutters and string winders. This tool does it all. The cutter works really well, as do the post remover and string winder.  The only thing I don't like is that you have to open the cutters each time you wish to cut. If you're used to spring loaded wire cutters, this can be annoying at first.

name: D'Addario Pro-Winder String Winder and Cutter
reviews: Good product and size

name: D'Addario Pro-Winder String Winder and Cutter
reviews: A simple tool that works well and makes restringing less of a chore. Excellent product.

name: D'Addario Pro-Winder String Winder and Cutter
reviews: Winding strings, ace. Cutting strings, ace.
